Notes
-----

This CVar was added on [version 1.2 of ETQW](Id_Tech_4 "Id Tech 4") . Caution:

-   This CVar should only be changed before a game is started.
-   This CVar should only be changed if you have a CPU with dual cores or better.
-   This CVar should not be set to "1" as that was only used for debugging.
-   This CVar should be set to "0" when running any mod tools or editors.
-   Setting this CVar to anything other than "0" may cause screenshots to be corrupted.


